(1330, 288, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"6c36fd69\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"64ccedcb\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"72f10239\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h1>\\u00a0<\\/h1><h1><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-285 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/whatsthedealpe.co.za\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/Voucher-Booklet-Cover-JPEGl-page-002-300x186.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"186\\\" \\/><\\/h1><h1><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-286 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/whatsthedealpe.co.za\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/Voucher-Booklet-Cover-JPEG-page-001-300x186.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"186\\\" \\/><\\/h1><h1>We are...<\\/h1><h1><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-127 alignright\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/whatsthedealpe.co.za\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/04\\/pocm01-4289166-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/h1><p><em><strong>What\'s The Deal PE,<\\/strong><\\/em> we are a local company based in Port Elizabeth looking to get you the best deals around.<br \\/>We will show you the weekly offers from local companies all in the convenience of one website, so no more hunting around for weekly specials or the best deals companies have to offer.\\u00a0\\u00a0We have them all here.<br \\/>Anything from... Where to eat, to where to take your car for the best deals, travel deals and where to stay, we will work hard on your behalf to get those deals<\\/p><h2><strong>We want all our deals to make you happy.<\\/strong><\\/h2><p><em><strong>What\'s the Deal PE<\\/strong><\\/em> can make things in life a little more affordable as we look for the best deals and offers at a price that\\u2019s hard to beat!<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-129 alignleft\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/whatsthedealpe.co.za\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/04\\/travel.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"225\\\" height=\\\"225\\\" \\/>We will only feature the best deals on the best restaurants, concerts, events, travel, spas, salons, retail shops, and much more.<\\/p><p><em><strong>What\'s The Deal PE<\\/strong><\\/em> is an online marketplace which connects local businesses to local customers.<br \\/>Customers use us to discover the best deals or offers on everything from weekly specials at your favourite restaurant to the best deal to get your car serviced, all to Port Elizabeth customers..<\\/p><p>We want to know what our customers want and what local businesses have to offer.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-128 alignright\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/whatsthedealpe.co.za\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/04\\/deal-300x65.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"65\\\" \\/><\\/p><h2>\\u00a0<\\/h2><h2><strong>Our Vision<\\/strong><\\/h2><p>Our vision is to see local businesses increasing their customer base and our customers getting the best and most affordable deals around<\\/p><h2><strong> Why Whats The Deal PE<\\/strong><\\/h2><p>We are a small, professional and personable company, looking to get the best deal for everyone. The Deals we offer, are deals we want to use, but Its not always about a great discount or more for free, its about trying something new or seeing a deal that makes something previously unattainable, affordable, or making something that is a necessity a bit less hard on the budget. We want people to get excited about looking on our website or thrilled when they get the voucher booklet, and see a deal that is just right for them.<br \\/>This site is a facility to let you know where all the best local deals are, we aren\\u2019t selling anything just giving you a helping hand.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\" wp-image-155 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/whatsthedealpe.co.za\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/04\\/early-bird-300x50.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"372\\\" height=\\\"62\\\" \\/><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
